.SH NAME
drm_client_dev_hotplug \- Send hotplug event to clients
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" drm_client_dev_hotplug
.BI "(struct drm_device *dev "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
DRM device
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This function calls the \fIdrm_client_funcs.hotplug\fP callback on the attached clients.

\fBdrm_kms_helper_hotplug_event\fP calls this function, so drivers that use it
don't need to call this function themselves.
